data.description: The feel of a cabin in the woods with west Knoxville amenities only minutes away.  Few homes sell in Wrights Ferry Landing because you are close to the lake and in a heavily wooded area.  Yet, West Town Mall is only 4 miles away.  This 2-story basement home is neatly tucked away in the trees on a private, one+ acre lot.  Numerous upgrades make it ready to move in and start enjoying such a quiet neighborhood. An inground pool and a jacuzzi are also surrounded by trees.  This is a perfect east Tennessee setting. New carpeting, woodburning fireplace, kitchen appliances, refinished wood floors and paint throughout.
